---
import Page from "../layout/page.astro";
---
<Page>
  <section class="hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Orb — Platform</p>
    <h1>
      <span class="word-bill">Bill</span>
      <span class="arrow">→</span>
      Build
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Stop writing billing code. Start shipping product.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="cards">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-media">
        <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," alt="Billing logic illustration" />
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <span class="card-tag">Before</span>
        <h2>Months building billing infrastructure</h2>
        <p>Entitlement checks scattered across your codebase. Pricing logic tangled with product logic. Every new plan means a new engineer sprint.</p>
        <div class="card-footer">
          <a href="#" class="card-arrow">Learn more ↗</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-media">
        <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," alt="Orb platform illustration" />
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <span class="card-tag">After</span>
        <h2>Ship pricing changes in minutes</h2>
        <p>Orb separates billing from your product code. Define plans in a dashboard. Deploy pricing experiments without touching your codebase.</p>
        <div class="card-footer">
          <a href="#" class="card-arrow">Get started ↗</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Page>

<style>
  /* Layout */
  .hero,
  .cards {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 3em;
  }

  /* Hero */
  .hero {
    padding-top: 7em;
    padding-bottom: 6em;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #666;
    margin: 0 0 1.5em;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(56px, 7vw, 92px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.0;
    color: #111;
    margin: 0 0 0.5em;
  }

  .word-bill {
    color: #ccc;
    text-decoration: line-through;
    text-decoration-color: #ccc;
  }

  .arrow {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.45em;
    color: #999;
    display: inline-block;
    vertical-align: middle;
    margin: 0 0.15em;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    color: #555;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Cards */
  .cards {
    padding-bottom: 7em;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5em;
  }

  .card {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    transition: transform 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease;
  }

  .card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.07);
  }

  .card-media img {
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
  }

  .card-body {
    padding: 2em;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75em;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .card-tag {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #666;
    border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 3px 8px;
    align-self: flex-start;
  }

  .card h2 {
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #111;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.25;
  }

  .card p {
    font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .card-footer {
    margin-top: auto;
    padding-top: 1em;
  }

  .card-arrow {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #111;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 8px 14px;
    display: inline-block;
    transition: background 0.12s ease, color 0.12s ease, border-color 0.12s ease;
  }

  .card-arrow:hover {
    background: #111;
    color: #fff;
    border-color: #111;
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .hero {
      padding-top: 4em;
      padding-bottom: 3em;
    }

    .cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      padding-bottom: 4em;
    }
  }
</style>
